    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325290/extras/1916e0c79c58e1fa2f9c0f4c988fe5b6.poster.avif?t=1772238230\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325290/extras/1916e0c79c58e1fa2f9c0f4c988fe5b6.webm?t=1772238230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>欢迎回家，孩子。 在这款社交冒险游戏中重拾赤子之心。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325290/extras/095e988e090e5d78d437ba2e51449a8b.poster.avif?t=1772238230\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325290/extras/095e988e090e5d78d437ba2e51449a8b.webm?t=1772238230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Sky 的国度在混沌中等待着你捎来希望的那一天。 向坠落地面且受困的先灵们传递光明，并拯救他们。 你的光芒将成为他们返还星空的力量。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《Sky光·遇》游戏特色</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325290/extras/6ba12ec9f6f49ba26902c62db60b5e65.poster.avif?t=1772238230\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325290/extras/6ba12ec9f6f49ba26902c62db60b5e65.webm?t=1772238230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>探索开放世界</strong><br>在这个暖心的国度，你可以随心自在地游玩。 无论是想进行刺激的冒险、与朋友闲聊，或者只是在阳光下放空，一切都由你决定。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325290/extras/bda707d422126e25dc96c9ed5e75707d.poster.avif?t=1772238230\" width=616 height=257 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325290/extras/bda707d422126e25dc96c9ed5e75707d.webm?t=1772238230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>无尽的冒险</strong><br>踏上任务，解决谜题，探索古代文明的废墟。起飞，交友，并经历试炼以打败黑暗。在游戏中的家中演奏音乐，参加音乐会，并举办派对。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325290/extras/f3b587a15dedecf743393ec6dbe238b4.poster.avif?t=1772238230\" width=616 height=321 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325290/extras/f3b587a15dedecf743393ec6dbe238b4.webm?t=1772238230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>隽永无边的故事</strong><br>踏上 Sky 国度之旅，你将遇到沉睡的废墟、神秘的壁画，它们乘载着遥远过去的辉煌与衰落。 那些因古代灾难而受困的先灵，正耐心等待你的释放。 透过散布各地的残影片段，逐步拼凑远古故事的原貌——以及你在这当中至关重要的角色。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325290/extras/a9e2172348aa9ff3dea870989e7e9b04.poster.avif?t=1772238230\" width=616 height=165 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325290/extras/a9e2172348aa9ff3dea870989e7e9b04.webm?t=1772238230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>尽情展现自我风格</strong><br>这个友善、包容的社群正引颈期盼着你的到来。 从时时更新的奇妙道具中任意挑选、搭配彰显您个性的装扮，展露当下心情。 使用可爱的表情，无需言语你即可与来自全球各地的朋友进行交流。 在 Sky 的世界里，你可以自在活出自我。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325290/extras/9e16717a8e055b3d89dbb75fcf1ebaac.poster.avif?t=1772238230\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325290/extras/9e16717a8e055b3d89dbb75fcf1ebaac.webm?t=1772238230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>在游玩中与社群连结</strong><br>环顾四周，你会发现很多新朋友，无论是与你一样刚进入王国的光之子，或是久历风霜的资深玩家。 牵上他们的手，这群引路人将带你探访国度中的各种新奇事物！",
